description:
&nbsp;Raw FASTQ files of K562 RNA-seq libraries prepared using the uMRT 37/30 protocol and UHRR RNA-seq libraries prepared with uMRT of the publication Single-cell RNA-seq using UltraMarathonRT, included are : 

 &nbsp;Raw FASTQ files of K562 RNA-seq libraries prepared using the uMRT 37/30 protocol

 paired-end reads of cell1 - cell9 


 Raw FASTQ files of UHRR RNA-seq libraries prepared using uMRT

